<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>死老虎躺在毛克利的脚边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须快点弄。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利对阿克拉和格瑞布拉德说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想把老虎的皮放在会议的岩石上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们开始准备虎皮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，狼们飞快地跑开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利感到一只手紧紧抓住了他的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥拿着枪站在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只老虎的皮是我的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猎人大声说道，“悬赏虎皮的钱很多。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利转了一下眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我相信你打算给我一些奖励。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是最棒的猎手。”布尔迪奥说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会给你任何奖励。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你抓住老虎只是因为运气好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走近老虎，俯身仔细地看着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这只老虎和我是宿敌。”毛克利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他挥了挥手。“阿克拉！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几秒钟后，布尔迪奥发现自己躺在草地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只大灰狼站在他身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥惊讶地眨了眨眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利召唤了一只狼！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是最坏的巫术！”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他吓坏了，像石头一样一动不动地躺着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果毛克利召唤更多的狼，怎么办？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>或者他把他自己变成狼或老虎？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伟大的国王。”布尔迪奥终于低声说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯？”毛克利笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，猎人害怕他了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是个老人。我不知道你这么厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我可以起来吗？你的狼会把我撕成碎片吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你走吧。但从现在起，别来烦我。”毛克利回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放他走，阿克拉。”他命令道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥一瘸一拐飞快地向村庄走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每隔几分钟，他就紧张地回头看看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他回到村里时，告诉村民们他看到了什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利和狼们完成了准备虎皮的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利把它藏在一棵树旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他聚集起水牛群，把它们都带回了村庄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他走近时，听见了很大的铃声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好像半个村庄的人都在门口等着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“村民们很高兴我杀了老虎。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利骄傲地自言自语，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们一定在等着感谢我呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，一块块石头从毛克利耳边呼啸而过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>愤怒的喊声不停地传来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巫师！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“森林恶魔！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开枪打死他，布尔迪奥！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那把旧枪嘡的一声响了起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但子弹没有打中毛克利，而是打中了一头水牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那男孩儿又使用巫术了！”一个村民喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他用巫术把子弹转了过去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村民们向毛克利扔了更多的石头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他弯下身子躲闪，努力不惊慌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉和格瑞布拉德跑到他身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就像狼群一样。”阿克拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们希望你走，毛克利。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“上次我被赶走因为我是人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这次因为我是狼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，麦苏雅从人群中跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的儿子！你的巫术故事是真的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当更多的石头在他头上呼啸而过时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利弯腰躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是巫师，麦苏雅，你知道的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你必须在他们伤害你之前离开！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有几个人朝空中挥舞着拳头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“离巫师远点儿，麦苏雅！”他们喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“回到这儿来，不然我们也会用石头砸你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利迅速拥抱了一下麦苏雅，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>感谢麦苏雅对自己的好意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他和两只狼从人类村庄逃走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>